    "description": "<p>Curly's is an exciting new pre-opening concept under the renowned Ebb &amp; Flow Group. With a focus on delivering delicious, sustainable café food, Curly's aims to create a unique dining experience that celebrates organic, locally sourced ingredients while promoting eco-friendly practices. Our mission is to provide a welcoming space where guests can enjoy thoughtfully crafted meals that not only support local farmers but also contribute to a healthier planet. As we prepare for our grand opening, we're looking for passionate individuals to join our team and help bring this exciting, sustainable vision to life.</p>",
